00:11:49.260 --> 00:11:52.260
(Video)JH: U redu idemo u pregovore od sada. Krenite.

00:11:52.260 --> 00:11:59.260
(Žamor)

00:12:00.260 --> 00:12:03.260
JH: Moje pitanje vama je, tko upravlja tom učionicom?

00:12:04.260 --> 00:12:07.260
